<i><c.white>plus jamais être ninja...</c></i>

00:16:21.820 --> 00:16:24.290
Cent quatre-vingt-quinze,

00:16:29.360 --> 00:16:31.890
196,

00:16:34.260 --> 00:16:37.300
197,

00:16:39.940 --> 00:16:42.470
198...

00:16:45.810 --> 00:16:48.740
